OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778004669
OL,3,CPeople left without postal votes days
OL,4,Cbefore Senedd election
OL,6,FA Welsh council says it will hand-
OL,7,Fdeliver postal vote packs after an
OL,8,Fissue with a "supplementary print run"
OL,9,Fleft some voters without them just
OL,10,Fdays out from the Senedd election.
OL,12,FCardiff Council said it has been
OL,13,Fworking urgently to investigate after
OL,14,Fsome voters reported that they had not
OL,15,Freceived their postal vote packs.
OL,17,FThe issue has affected voters in the
OL,18,FCaerdydd Ffynnon Taf and Caerdydd
OL,19,FPenarth constituencies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
