PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778004669
OL,3,CPeople left without postal votes days
OL,4,Cbefore Senedd election
OL,6,FThe council said replacements will
OL,7,Feither be hand-delivered on Tuesday, 5
OL,8,FMay, or sent using priority mail.
OL,10,FA council spokesman said the council
OL,11,Fhad issued almost 47,000 postal vote
OL,12,Fpacks in recent weeks and that, to
OL,13,Fdate, more than 26,500 have already
OL,14,Fbeen returned.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778004669
OL,3,CPeople left without postal votes days
OL,4,Cbefore Senedd election
OL,6,F"Following reports from some voters
OL,7,Fthat they hadn't yet received their
OL,8,Fpostal vote packs we have been working
OL,9,Furgently to investigate the issue and
OL,10,Fhave identified that the affected
OL,11,Fpacks relate to a supplementary print
OL,12,Frun for the Caerdydd Ffynnon Taf and
OL,13,FCaerdydd Penarth constituencies," they
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"We have received assurances from our
OL,17,Fprint provider, Civica, that the
OL,18,Frelevant data was received correctly
OL,19,Ffrom the council and that the packs
OL,20,Fwere printed and dispatched to Royal
OL,21,FMail who continue to investigate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778004669
OL,3,CPeople left without postal votes days
OL,4,Cbefore Senedd election
OL,6,F"In response to inquiries from
OL,7,Findividual voters we have already
OL,8,Freissued a number of postal vote packs.
OL,10,F"Replacement packs will be hand-
OL,11,Fdelivered to the remaining affected
OL,12,Fhouseholds on Tuesday, May 5, with a
OL,13,Fsmall number reissued by priority mail.
OL,15,F"Voters who receive a replacement pack
OL,16,Fcan complete it and either return it
OL,17,Fto our staff at the time of delivery,
OL,18,Fhand it in at any polling station
OL,19,Fbefore 10pm on Thursday, or deliver it
OL,20,Fto County Hall before 10pm on polling
OL,21,Fday.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
